Trivial String Test Project

- This project has 4 main components

1. Server
2. Client
3. Ethereum
4. Nginx

Run docker-compose up to run entire project

Smart contract is deployed using the Kovan test network on Infura.

Required Updates:-

1. Remove hard coded values in ethereum project and add them to environment variables
2. Write automated tests for client and server
3. Update Smart Contract tests to include event emission
4. Automate contract deployment and getting abi information
5. Setup Swagger for backend api
6. Remove hard coded gas value and allow user to input gas value

I left variables in the test repo incase you want to try running to project.
